1.0.name: connect20/MailChimp_EComm360
1.0.description:
The MailChimp Ecommerce Tracking Plugin helps you measure the
ROI of your email campaigns. We'll track when people click from your email
campaigns, visit your website, all the way to purchase. Then we'll aggregate
the information and display it on your MailChimp campaign report.
